## E.50 Really final

Reader-time introspection: three verbs, one pipeline, infinite tools.

Every custom source-processing tool a Motoi programmer might build starts with `(parse src)`. From there the introspection layer takes over, and the specific tool is whatever transformation the programmer needs.

Small primitive. Large surface. That is Motoi.

